c: 10
v: 67
t: "hw aladhi jaeal lakum -ayha alnas- allayl litaskunuu fih wthdwu min eana' alharakat fi talab almeash, wajaeal lakum alnhar; ltbsru fyh, wltseawa litalab rzqkm. 'iina fi akhtilaf allayl walnahar wahal ahlhma fihima ladlaltan whjjana ealaa 'ana allah wahdah hu almsthq llebadt, liqawm yasmaeun hadhih alhjj, wayatafakarun fyha"